   596 				; Return mirrors the joystick fire button: save the patch, but only while the
   597 				; PRESET param is selected. Keep prev_preset in sync so preset_tick won't reload.
   598 22AA			nav_save_preset
   599 22AA AD 00 06		        lda cur_param
